---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service - Home Town Web Host"
  description="Review the Home Town Web Host terms of service. Understand our policies on hosting services, acceptable use, and customer obligations."
>
  <section class="section page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="page-meta">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-wrapper">
      <h2>Agreement to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing or using Home Town Web Host's website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
      </p>

      <h2>Services Description</h2>
      <p>
        Home Town Web Host provides web hosting services including basic hosting, AI-enabled hosting, and custom hosting solutions for small businesses and individuals. Service features and availability may vary by plan.
      </p>

      <h2>Account Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>
        You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use.
      </p>

      <h2>Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to use our services to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Host content that is illegal, harmful, or infringes on intellectual property rights</li>
        <li>Distribute malware, spam, or engage in phishing activities</li>
        <li>Consume excessive server resources that impact other customers</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or other accounts</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Payment Terms</h2>
      <p>
        All prices are listed in US dollars. Payment is due at the beginning of each billing cycle. We accept major credit cards and other payment methods as indicated during signup. Promotional pricing is valid until the stated expiration date.
      </p>

      <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all new hosting plans. After the 30-day period, refunds are provided at our discretion. Setup fees and domain registration fees are non-refundable.
      </p>

      <h2>Service Availability</h2>
      <p>
        We strive to maintain 99.9% uptime for all hosting services. Scheduled maintenance will be communicated in advance. We are not liable for downtime caused by factors outside our control.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        Home Town Web Host shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by you for the service during the twelve months preceding the claim.
      </p>

      <h2>Termination</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your account for violation of these terms. You may cancel your account at any time by contacting our support team.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may modify these terms at any time. Material changes will be communicated via email or website notice. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .page-meta {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2);
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .content-wrapper h2 {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

  .content-wrapper h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

  .content-wrapper ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-6);
  }

  .content-wrapper li {
    list-style: disc;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-wrapper a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
